Job Description
We are actively seeking customer focused Call Center Representatives/Sales Executives to fill several positions. Qualified candidates are encouraged to apply. The successful candidate will be customer centric, will have excellent follow-up skills and have the ability to multi-task in a fast paced environment.Please apply if you are able to work a NIGHT SHIFT and have tele sales / telemarketing experience.Fresh candidate will be considered !
Job Specification
Excellent Grammar Ability to work a NIGHT SHIFT. Spelling and Punctuation. Command on US/Canadian Accent Hard working Self-motivated Ability to understand, analyze and solve problems Candidate must be Vibrant / Energetic /Enthusiastic Strong verbal and written communication skills Ability to integrate with an existing team and thrive in a rapidly changing environment. Excellent follow-up skills and ability to meet aggressive deadlines. Working knowledge of MS Office.
Must be reliable to fulfill shift. Commitment to stay with the Company for a period of at least 1 year.
